        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-10-26 17:17:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWe need a new pom.xml entry:\n\n  <groupId>org.onap.logging-analytics.pomba</groupId>\n  <artifactId>pomba-audit-common</artifactId>\n  <version>1.4.1-SNAPSHOT</version>\n  <packaging>jar</packaging>",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "af962a6e150c52fd547b55b08c8478dfb103c821",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2015,
          "name": "Geora Barsky",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "georab@amdocs.com",
          "username": "georab"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-10-26 17:23:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWhy we need 1.4.1-SNAPSHOT version ? Is 1.4.0-SNAPSHOT wrong version ?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "f0a0ed8407c0444204dbd00e948d2b780e3725cf",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3479,
          "name": "Prudence Au",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "prudence.au@amdocs.com",
          "username": "pau2882"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-10-26 18:48:16.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDublin is 1.4.x and this is our first version of audit-common in Dublin so 1.4.0-SNAPSHOT should be fine.  And this is already done as part of introducing the Dublin/Master branch.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "94985e8d786135430524d6fdfb62f7a99313771f",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3131,
          "name": "Trevor Tait",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "rtait@amdocs.com",
          "username": "rtait"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-10-26 18:51:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI thought some of our context builders may already be using 1.4.0, but this should not be the case, so we are fine.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "6e8be1840fa827cc4dfdeb11adb68d62f7fbc844",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3479,
          "name": "Prudence Au",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "prudence.au@amdocs.com",
          "username": "pau2882"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-10-26 18:55:07.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n@Trevor, SDNC uses 1.4.x for Casablanca.  So, sdnc/apps was released with 1.4.x.  But POMBA is still using 1.3.x for Casablanca.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "22198100d925f44f8ad0731a4c3f60923a5ceb74",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3131,
          "name": "Trevor Tait",
